📘 Looped Operations Wiki

Official documentation for Looped Operations — a Roblox-based nuclear facility simulation focused on realism, control systems, and operator procedures.

---

⚙️ About

The Looped Operations Wiki serves as the central knowledge base for all systems within the facility, including:

- Reactor operation procedures
- Control room systems and interfaces
- Emergency response protocols
- Engineering and maintenance references

This documentation is designed to support both new operators and experienced personnel.

---

🏭 Project Overview

Looped Operations is a detailed simulation of an Advanced Gas-cooled Reactor (AGR) environment built on Roblox.

The goal of this project is to provide:

- 🔬 Realistic reactor behaviour
- 🎛️ Interactive control systems
- 🚨 Emergency scenario training
- 🧠 Educational insight into nuclear operations

---

📚 Wiki Structure

The wiki is organised into structured sections:

- 🖥️ General — Core information and control room basics
- ⚙️ Guides — Step-by-step operational procedures
- 🚨 Emergency Procedures — Critical response documentation
- 🔧 Systems — Detailed breakdowns of plant systems

Navigation is automatically generated using page metadata ("nav_group" and "nav_order").

---

✍️ Contributing

Contributions are welcome.

To add or edit pages:

1. Create a new ".md" file inside "/wiki/pages/"
2. Add frontmatter:

---
title: Page Title
layout: wiki
nav_group: guides
nav_order: 1
---

3. Write content using Markdown
4. Commit and push changes

The sidebar and search will update automatically.

---

